data.title: Register of Solicitors 20230911 S Z Corrected v2
data.meta_description: Register-of-Solicitors-20230911-S-Z-corrected-v2 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document is a register of solicitors in Queensland as of 11/09/2023. It lists solicitors' first and last names, middle initials, practising certificate type (restricted or unrestricted, principal or employee), any conditions on their certificate, specialist accreditation areas, employer name and address, and their date of admission to practice law. There are over 100 solicitors listed with varying levels of experience, employers, and locations of practice across Queensland.
